        </ul>
        <p><strong>YOLOv8 Action:</strong> Override for ambulance right-of-way.<br>
          LED: <em>‚ÄúEmergency Vehicle Passing ‚Äî Please Wait‚Äù</em> ‚Üí Safe to Cross</p>
      </div>
    </section>

